fields.title: Suicide of Sushant
fields.body:
Suicide of Sushant Singh Rajput has triggered  discussions on the nepotism nature of Bollywood.
People are discussing  how is it difficult to settle in Bollywood if one is a outsider(means having no godfather in Bollywood). Director Karan Johar is being targeted because of the reason he has been seen making joke of late Sushant.

fields.title: YouTube channels to learn Python
fields.body:
I have listed some of the YouTube channels to learn python and its frameworks.
1. Corey Schafer: Python playlist on this channel is comprehensive, covering almost every bit of python. You can also learn Django on this channel by developing a project.
2. CodingForEnterpreneurs: This channel 
   is good as Corey Schafer channel. 
   Apart from providing python guide, it also provides 
   a comprehensive guide to Django, the most popular 
   Python Web Framework.
3. Dennis Lvy: This channel mainly focuses on teaching 
   Django thoroughly. It has a also a lecture on Django 
   Rest Framework. You can also find projects built in 
   Django on this channel.

fields.title: Pavan Shetty, Director Of Porsche India, Resigns
fields.body: Pavan Shetty, Director Porsche India has resigned from his position on July 1, 2020 citing personal reasons. In the interim, Ashish Kaul – Head of Sales, Porsche India will assume responsibility for day-to-day operations at Porsche India and will report directly to Mr Gurpratap Boparai, Managing Director Skoda Auto Volkswagen India for Strategic initiatives. An announcement on the permanent replacement will be made in due course of time.

fields.title: Visit to Hyderabad
fields.body:
Hyderabad is one of the oldest cities of India. It was merged in India after a military operation in 1948. Before this, it was ruled by Nizam of Hyderabad. The popular places to visit in Hyderabad are
1. Charminar
2. Macca Masjid
3. Salar Jung Museum
4. Golconda Fort
5. Hussain Sagar Lake
6. Snow World.
